Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:36.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在雪中散去的再不斩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.80,0:01:39.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.33,0:01:42.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里干吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了这么多人又是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思了 再不斩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就请你死在这儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.11,0:02:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果请正规忍者 可是要花很多钱的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才会雇佣你们这些叛忍
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.05,0:02:10.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能顺便让你们这些忍者互相残杀的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以节约我很多金钱和时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:18.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么雾隐鬼人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我眼里不过是个滑稽的小丑罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.19,0:02:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙从哪儿冒出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.40,0:02:35.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然我不用去杀达兹纳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.25,0:02:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再跟你打下去也没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.61,0:02:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.49,0:02:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子跟我还有点有过节呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然害本大爷骨折
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 这小子已经死了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋 想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.70,0:03:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.85,0:03:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要轻举妄动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是开口说话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.66,0:03:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.25,0:03:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的遗体被那样糟蹋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.52,0:03:25.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一点感觉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你忘了他一直伴随在你左右吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.52,0:03:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就像是卡多在利用我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也只是在利用白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.85,0:03:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们忍者只不过是工具
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要的 是他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而不是他的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:51.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…毫无依恋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:57.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…真的这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这样 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.43,0:04:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们与他的战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.80,0:04:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:04.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.59,0:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是我的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.89,0:04:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打从心底喜欢你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.98,0:04:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有很重要的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是那么地喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当一个人一心想保护重要的东西时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就真的可以变强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的一点感觉都没有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要成为真正的忍者是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.45,0:04:43.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.03,0:04:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的完全不在乎他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:49.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:52.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此 我愿意成为真正的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想变得像你一样厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是却只得到这种结果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.00,0:05:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己的命都不要了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要实现他的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:11.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…就是我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连自己的梦想也没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:18.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能像工具一样死去…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.03,0:05:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在是太残酷了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:36.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要再说下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.28,0:06:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白不只是为了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:10.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是为了你们才决意要战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我比谁都清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.01,0:06:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:22.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够跟你们交手真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者也是人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许无法成为没有感情的工具…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.23,0:06:46.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我输了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼 把你的苦无借给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 你们快去干掉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为靠自己一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.17,0:07:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能打赢这么多人吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:56.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鬼…鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.61,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然那么想见同伴的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.39,0:08:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就自己一个人去吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并没打算…跟白去同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么…你还想逞强…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:40.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和本大爷一起…下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:46.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雾隐鬼人下了地狱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:50.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以变成真正的鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:53.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我究竟是不是小丑到地狱就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.09,0:09:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了…白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.27,0:10:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一路走来 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别转头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一个努力活下去的男人最后的尊严
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.31,0:10:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.31,0:10:47.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 你好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.44,0:10:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐…助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.02,0:11:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.38,0:11:06.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.03,0:11:07.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.32,0:11:09.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱…好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:16.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不可以动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 鸣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那个戴面具的家伙呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.59,0:11:29.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过那个戴面具的少年已经死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被鸣人杀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.02,0:11:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我也不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.14,0:11:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他为了掩护再不斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都相信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:47.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是佐助 躲过了致命伤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙打从一开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.92,0:11:54.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.62,0:11:58.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助没事了 他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白也是为了你们才决意要战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.53,0:12:20.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是个老好人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.19,0:12:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:26.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下放心了 佐助也平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.97,0:12:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们开心得太早了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.13,0:12:36.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们好不容易找到的雇主就这么被杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.79,0:12:42.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然如此 我们干脆袭击城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把值钱的东西都拿走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.19,0:12:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.97,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一下子就能解决这些人的忍术吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我消耗了太多的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们敢再靠近这座岛一步
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就要动用所有的武力了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.48,0:13:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们有来无回
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.70,0:13:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.14,0:13:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英雄总是迟一些登场的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.71,0:13:23.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙们…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.38,0:13:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也来助你们一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.42,0:13:42.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种程度的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我现在的查克拉也能虚张声势一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.69,0:13:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西版
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来啊 动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.66,0:13:58.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:08.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.98,0:14:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西 有件事想拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:38.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.09,0:14:45.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…再看看那家伙的脸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.81,0:14:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.57,0:15:21.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种季节竟然会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.89,0:15:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.28,0:15:34.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哭泣吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:57.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直以来 你都在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.78,0:16:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少…最后时刻让我能在你身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.32,0:16:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的…想和你去同一个地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.17,0:16:53.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.67,0:16:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是出生在一个白雪皑皑的村子里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.48,0:17:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就像雪一样洁白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.27,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的 再不斩…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.81,0:17:15.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会在一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.84,0:17:27.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者存在意义真的像他们说的一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.06,0:17:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以追寻自身存在的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.34,0:17:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要像工具那样存在才是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.45,0:17:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这点连我们木叶也不例外
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.48,0:17:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所谓真正的忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.39,0:17:56.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这么想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以忍者都不知觉地活在这个困扰中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像再不斩和那个孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.11,0:18:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.46,0:18:21.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走我自己的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.98,0:18:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一条绝对不会后悔的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.41,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇往直前地走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托各位的福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大桥已经建成了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:50.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会非常寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:53.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢各位的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达兹纳大叔 我还会再来玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊那利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.95,0:19:10.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也会觉得很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:13.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想哭就哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁要哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:18.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥才是 想哭就哭嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.63,0:19:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:34.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 就爱逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.07,0:19:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年改变了伊那利的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.64,0:19:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊那利改变了村民的心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.28,0:19:53.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个少年为我们搭建了迈向希望的勇气之桥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,桥啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.70,0:19:57.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到桥的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.94,0:20:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没给大桥取名呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.15,0:20:01.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:06.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然想到一个超级适合这座桥的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.58,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫“鸣人大桥”如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好名字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.53,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要赶快回去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让伊鲁卡老师请我吃拉面庆祝任务完成
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 还有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.11,0:20:27.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要让木叶丸知道我的英勇事迹才行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 回村之后跟我约会好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:35.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.15,0:20:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我约会吧 我随时奉陪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死人了 鸣人 你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.33,0:20:45.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.57,0:20:47.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要取这个名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.68,0:20:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望这座大桥永远都不会垮掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:21:02.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且有一天会成为举世闻名的大桥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.29,0:21:08.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才要叫这个名字啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.48,0:22:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:56.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们第七班最近老是执行一些简单的任务啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:23:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们明明打败了\N像再不斩和白那样厉害的忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.09,0:23:05.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没什么更能让我施展身手的任务吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.45,0:23:08.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我的忍道和心都燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.87,0:23:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.71,0:23:13.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的篇章 晋级中忍的考试
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.13,0:23:16.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的忍道
